We have three cats, the youngest is about eleven years old, another is fifteen and our oldest is, well ancient. That is what the vet told us; however, if she said a kitten or a kitten by a litter of kittens, then I would have to guess that our oldest is about seventeen years old.

One of the cats has very thin and wrinkled skin, and the vet said the skin was not suitable for a kitten. We love your product and want you to change to no-burn harvesting so we can continue to buy
